data.description: $10,000 SELLER INCENTIVES! BEACHSIDE LIVING with LOTS of SPACE and PRIVACY for everyone!!  4 Bedrooms and 3 FULL Baths which include separate living quarters for guests or multi-generational needs. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and an oversized window offering a view of the amazing backyard OASIS!  This home is where you want to be with its meticulously designed landscaping along the generous sized backyard surrounding a relaxing and refreshing pool.  Entertain under the charming gazebo with an outdoor kitchen.  This coastal designed home has a NEWER METAL ROOF, HURRICANE IMPACT DOORS & Windows in owners additional suite, shutters elsewhere, SOLAR PANELS and beautifully paved, oversized circular driveway with plenty of room to park extra vehicles, boat or RV!  Steps from Florida's beautiful beaches, you're surrounded by fabulous restaurants, local shops and easy access to the highway.  Let your beachside living begin!
